### List reroute candidates (replace <token> and {prescriptionId})
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/prescriptions/customer/{{prescriptionId}}/reroute/candidates?excludePharmacyId={{originalPharmacyId}}&lat={{lat}}&lng={{lng}}&radiusKm=10&limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{customer_token}}

### Reroute unavailable items to a single pharmacy
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/prescriptions/customer/{{prescriptionId}}/reroute
Authorization: Bearer {{customer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: {{uuid}}

{
  "originalPharmacyId": {{originalPharmacyId}},
  "parentPreviewId": "PP-2025-001239",
  "targetPharmacyId": {{targetPharmacyId}},
  "note": "Please try to fulfill these if available.",
  "items": [
    { "name": "Amoxicillin 500mg", "quantity": 1 },
    { "name": "Cetirizine 10mg", "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "strategy": "SINGLE"
}

### Reroute to multiple pharmacies (broadcast)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/prescriptions/customer/{{prescriptionId}}/reroute
Authorization: Bearer {{customer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: {{uuid}}

{
  "originalPharmacyId": {{originalPharmacyId}},
  "parentPreviewId": "PP-2025-001239",
  "targetPharmacyIds": [{{id1}}, {{id2}}],
  "note": "Broadcasting unavailable items",
  "items": [
    { "name": "Amoxicillin 500mg", "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "strategy": "BROADCAST"
}

